item.title: CVE-2024-4304|2024-08-01T20:33:53.199Z -- gt3%20soluciones -- swal
item.description: A Cross-Site Scripting XSS vulnerability has been detected on GT3 Soluciones SWAL. This vulnerability consists in a reflected XSS in the Titular parameter inside Gestion 'Documental > Seguimiento de Expedientes > Alta de Expedientes'.
